<p>3、一如既往孤独相伴，千万纷扰与我何干。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//35ea/35ea96264702b23a6f4b346422d096fc.com/large/18520005a3f407f1a529"></p> 
<p>4、想家的时候。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//620c/620c20d9363cc69ee2222b01c2f77411.com/large/17f60003404309779843"></p> 
<p>5、不会在你遭受非议之时转身离开。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//7975/7975080bcbe2e5f7d7f83e430e0e25ea.com/large/17f6000340429a7cdc95"></p> 
<p>6、走的最急的是最美的风景，伤的最深的是最真的感情。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//b93c/b93c628d250d804566804cd57df53c5b.com/large/17f10006f62911f7ef9c"></p> 
<p>7、那些无关风花雪月的相思，说来几人能知。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//abc7/abc7ab6d40c83ad40f3d93794fece013.com/large/17f600034045594c9c30"></p> 
<p>8、从容是真 宽释是福 有敬无畏 乐以忘优。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//f7e0/f7e0f7151820b154c355e41cb322a4a1.com/large/17f600034044902684f6"></p> 
<p>9、创造自己想要的生活。</p> 
<p><img src="http://113.31.136.132:8081//9a1f/9a1f6a31fc703f0634a352263e46178c.com/large/17f10006f62d724a3221"></p> 
